  "helpFaqQ1": "Why isn't my streak counting up?",
  "helpFaqA1": "A streak advances when you complete a session on a new day. Extra sessions on the same day do not add another day, and one missed day can be covered by the weekly freeze token for that ISO week.",
  "helpFaqQ2": "How do I change reminder times?",
  "helpFaqA2": "Open Settings, go to Notifications, and tap the time subtitle on an enabled reminder row to open the time picker.",
  "helpFaqQ3": "Can I listen offline?",
  "helpFaqA3": "Yes. Tap Download on any library session, then use the Offline filter in the Library to see what is saved on this device.",
  "helpFaqQ4": "How do I switch language or theme?",
  "helpFaqA4": "Open Settings and look in the Account section for Language and Theme.",
  "helpFaqQ5": "What happens when I delete my account?",
  "helpFaqA5": "Serenity clears the local progress, reminders, and other saved data on this device. Cloud accounts and sync are not live yet, so there is no remote account data to remove.",
  "helpFaqQ6": "Is this medical advice?",
  "helpFaqA6": "No. Serenity is a wellness app, not medical care. If you need that reminder again, open the Wellness disclaimer row in Settings.",
